    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>青春之泉已被秘藏。然天命已定，终有一位篡位者将斩尽永恒者，重现神泉于世。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《FOUNTAINS》 -《永泉传说》是一款动作角色扮演游戏，在这个迷宫般相连的世界里，玩家需以战斗开辟前路。你将化身戴着兜帽的神秘人，刚被暴虐的统治者投入牢狱。你能冲破囚笼，揭开这个战火纷飞的帝国背后的重重迷雾吗？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.poster.avif?t=1769777114\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.webm?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.mp4?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《永泉传说》的世界宛如一座庞大的地宫，错综复杂的通道时而分叉、时而回环。探索途中你将不断获得新的物品、能力与强化，以此开启世界的新篇章。  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《永泉传说》还设有独特的在线留言系统。你可以在各处留下提示，指引他人迷途，亦或是设下陷阱，让人堕入愚行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精进战斗技艺，在绝境中击败充满挑战的首领 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 获取各式能力与工具，用于护身兼探路 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 结识形形色色的角色，无不敌友难辨 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 处处皆藏玄机，一刻不可松懈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
